description:
This week on Unqualified, Anna and Sim sit down with Hollywood sweetheart Lauren Graham (Gilmore Girls, Parenthood)! They talk about typecasting, interviews, Valentine’s Day and Lauren’s book “Talking As Fast As I Can"! Lauren also has a run-in with Kayla and takes on some Deal Breakers! They then call Peter, who doesn’t know what to do when he falls in love with a man abroad, and Kirsten, whose husband is reluctant about her keeping her maiden name.

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
